 Agoura Hills 
</P>
<P>
 * On a few occasions recently I have watched Rush Limbaugh's TV show. I have 
noticed that the following people are never in Rush's audience of "dittoheads": 
</P>
<P>
 African Americans, Asians, Hispanics, males with long hair, males with beards, 
females in short skirts, males or females in T-shirts and males or females in 
