<P>
 Vandals punctured the tires on 15 cars in the Las Casitas neighborhood of 
Thousand Oaks early Thursday, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 Nine cars parked alongside the Las Casitas condominium complex and six more by 
the adjacent Mirabella Apartment complex had tires slashed, Ventura County 
