<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ropak Corp.: The Fullerton maker of plastic packaging and handling products 
posted a third-quarter profit of $1.2 million, or 23 cents a share.That was up 
from earnings of $392,000, or 9 cents a share, for the same period last year. 
Revenue increased 21% to $36 million from $29.7 million. Nine-month profit 
totaled $3.2 million, or 63 cents a share, compared to earnings of $1.7 
million, or 38 cents a share, for the same period last year. Nine-month revenue 
rose 19% to $96.9 million from $81.6 million. 
</P>
