<DOCNO> LA102894-0199 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 093044 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 28, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
